{"tid":1623950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登突然有班人好執著於死物","createTime":"2019-10-05T02:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:30:35.000Z","uid":288158,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"758b62115e314ef309050304d38cd52ee1ef9750","tid":1623950,"uid":288158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:24:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解咁似曾相識既</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日不停有人帶風向，有班人開始叫人唔好爆鋪，直到今日見到有人話勇武裝修係純粹發洩<br />\n<br />\n同當初神獸出現既時候一，勇武做野都係有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前因後果</span></span>  ，爆親既店、神獸得既人有邊D唔係抵死？<br />\n<br />\n被爆鋪既唔係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">鄉黑店</span>就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">中資紅底</span>同埋<span style=\"font-size: large;\">垃圾黨鐵</span>，有無因為間鋪既政見係藍就裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有最重要既原則，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">爆鋪但唔搶野</span></span>，因為我地唔係暴徒，過去係咁，一直都會係咁<br />\n<br />\n然後又有人出Po中共就係想抹黑我地做暴徒，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喂大佬，訓左幾撚耐呀？我地和理非果陣已經比人屈做暴徒啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地可以玩到依加既原因係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">國際文宣做解釋</span>，冚世界都知中共無賴，佢點諗關我地撚事？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a4176e6aa4475f072c4c2c94ee2cd2996da7c9","tid":1623950,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:25:29.000Z","msg":"10月5全城休息一日"},{"pid":"ffb888ebe3cca0c80f0257461144673278aa7112","tid":1623950,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:26:00.000Z","msg":"林鄭黑警你估冇acc?"},{"pid":"e5cbd7c680c2a1993d8ddd158e697d5945869c4c","tid":1623950,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:26:33.000Z","msg":"但有啲藍紅不分，搞埋藍底呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110e2c57153429